11#ifndef COMMON_AUDIO_WINDOW_GENERATOR_H_
12#define COMMON_AUDIO_WINDOW_GENERATOR_H_
13
14#include <stddef.h>
15
16namespace webrtc {
17
18// Helper class with generators for various signal transform windows.
19class WindowGenerator {
20 public:
21 WindowGenerator() = delete;
22 WindowGenerator(const WindowGenerator&) = delete;
23 WindowGenerator& operator=(const WindowGenerator&) = delete;
24
25 static void Hanning(int length, float* window);
26 static void KaiserBesselDerived(float alpha, size_t length, float* window);
27};
28
29} // namespace webrtc
30
31#endif // COMMON_AUDIO_WINDOW_GENERATOR_H_
